  <name>VacuumTube</name>
  <summary>YouTube for TV, on your PC</summary>
  <developer id="rocks.shy">
    <name>shy</name>
  </developer>
  <metadata_license>CC0-1.0</metadata_license>
  <project_license>MIT</project_license>
  <update_contact>shy+vacuumtube@shy.rocks</update_contact>
  <description>
    <p>VacuumTube is an unofficial open source wrapper of YouTube Leanback (the console and Smart TV version of YouTube) for PCs, with a built-in adblocker and other enhancements. It is the best way to experience YouTube on your media center or handheld PC!</p>
  </description>
